# Any egg-info anywhere in the repo. A maintainer running `pip install -e .`
# locally leaves ghostbit.egg-info/ at the root, which would otherwise be
# COPY-ed into the image and shadow the real dist-info that pip installs,
# making importlib.metadata resolve to the pre-install version.
**/*.egg-info
.venv
venv
